were all fighting together,

00:02:04.791 --> 00:02:08.027
or not necessarily together,
but to try and defeat Assad.

00:02:08.027 --> 00:02:09.429
- Opposite.

00:02:09.429 --> 00:02:10.597
- It's the opposite.

00:02:10.597 --> 00:02:12.265
