lady here, Mrs. Lina Sergie.

00:15:05.204 --> 00:15:07.072
I would like to give
it to you with some--

00:15:07.072 --> 00:15:08.774
- It's astonishing.

00:15:08.774 --> 00:15:12.011 align:start size:94% position:6%
This is a book of 100,000
that have been killed

00:15:12.011 --> 00:15:14.013
during this terrible war,
and you were telling me

00:15:14.013 --> 00:15:16.115 align:start size:97% position:3%
that there are another
100,000 that they could put--

00:15:16.115 --> 00:15:19.385 align:start size:84% position:16%
- Now it's over
than 200,000 people.

00:15:19.385 --> 00:15:22.554
- Well here's the hope that
there will be no more books,

00:15:22.554 --> 00:15:25.190 align:start size:97% position:3%
and that you will find the
peace that you're looking for.

00:15:25.190 --> 00:15:26.292 align:start size:84% position:16%
I really appreciate
you being here.

